  "text": "The paper is organized as follows: in Section 2 we introduce the variational formulation of the problem and we recall a generalized version of Weierstrass theorem, Mazur theorem and a convexity criterion. Moreover, we recall a variant of the symmetric mountain pass theorem for \"subquadratic\" problems stated in [CITATION_1] . In Section 3 we prove Theorem 1.1 and in Section 4 we show Theorem 1.2.",
