    "123031691": {
      "title": "A critical point theorem related to the symmetric mountain pass lemma and its applications to elliptic equations",
      "abstract": "Abstract For an even functional on a Banach space, the symmetric mountain pass lemma gives a sequence of critical values which converges to zero. Under the same assumptions on the functional, this paper establishes a new critical point theorem which provides a sequence of critical points converging to zero. The theorem is applied to sublinear elliptic equations. Then a sequence of solutions converging to zero is obtained."
